@startuml AD_LT_02_Record_Embryo_Development

title AD_LT_02 — Record Embryo Development & Cryopreservation

|Lab Technician|
|System|

|Lab Technician|

note
  Prerequisites:
  - AD_LT_00 User Authenticated
  - AD_LT_01 Active IVF cycle exists
  - Technician assigned to this cycle
end note

start

:Open Embryology Module;
:Search and select patient's active cycle;

|System|

:Display embryo list with\nlatest data + doctor instructions;

|Lab Technician|

:Select embryo to update;
:Enter observation data:\n- Development day\n- Cell count\n- Fragmentation %\n- Morphology grade (Gardner)\n- Free-text notes;

|System|

if (Mandatory fields complete?\n(day, cell count, grade)) then (no)
  :Block submission;\nHighlight missing fields;
  |Lab Technician|
  :Correct missing fields;
  |System|
else (yes)
endif

if (Value outside expected range?) then (yes)
  :Warn technician;\nAllow entry with\nmandatory confirmation note;
  |Lab Technician|
  :Confirm deviation with note;
  |System|
else (no)
endif

:Save entry as immutable;\nTimestamp + technician ID;
:Update doctor and patient dashboards;

|Lab Technician|

if (Attach microscopy image?) then (yes)
  if (Image ≤ 10 MB?) then (no)
    :Show size error;
    :Skip image upload;
  else (yes)
    :Upload microscopy image;
  endif
else (no)
endif

if (Freeze embryo?) then (yes)
  :Enter cryopreservation details:\n- Storage tank\n- Cane\n- Straw position\n- Freezing date\n- Vitrification method;

  |System|

  :Record cryopreservation event;\nSet embryo status = Frozen;
  :Link storage location\nto embryo record;

  |Lab Technician|

else (no)
endif

if (Doctor freeze/transfer\ninstruction present?) then (yes)
  |System|
  :Highlight doctor instruction\nprominently;
  |Lab Technician|
else (no)
endif

:Confirm submission;

stop

@enduml
